<servcat id="30">
<name>ENGINE</name>
<section id="10006_S0004" variety="S0004">
<name>1TR-FE ENGINE CONTROL SYSTEM</name>
<ttl id="10006_S0004_7A7XX_T002B" variety="T002B">
<name>CRANKSHAFT POSITION SENSOR</name>
<para id="RM000000VX301MX" category="A" type-id="80001" name-id="ES45Z-03" from="201202">
<name>REMOVAL</name>
<subpara id="RM000000VX301MX_01" type-id="01" category="01">
<s-1 id="RM000000VX301MX_01_0001" proc-id="RM21Q0EV__000005D00000">
<ptxt>DISCONNECT CABLE FROM NEGATIVE BATTERY TERMINAL</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<atten2>
<ptxt>Wait at least 90 seconds after disconnecting the cable from the negative (-) battery terminal to prevent airbag activation.</ptxt>
</atten2>
</content1>
</s-1>
<s-1 id="RM000000VX301MX_01_0004" proc-id="RM21Q0EV__000005F00000">
<ptxt>REMOVE DRIVE BELT
</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<s2>
<ptxt>Use the hexagon-shaped part indicated by the arrow in the illustration to move the tensioner pulley downward and decrease the tension in the drive belt. Then remove the drive belt.</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="A099194E01" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
<atten3>
<ptxt>When removing the drive belt, do not use the idle pulley's bolt.</ptxt>
</atten3>
<atten4>
<ptxt>After removing the drive belt, move the tensioner upward to the maximum position.</ptxt>
</atten4>
</s2>
</content1></s-1>
<s-1 id="RM000000VX301MX_01_0005" proc-id="RM21Q0EV__000005G00000">
<ptxt>REMOVE COOLER COMPRESSOR ASSEMBLY</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<s2>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="A099198E02" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
<ptxt>Remove the 2 bolts and disconnect the suction hose from the engine.</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="G039332E03" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
<ptxt>Disconnect the cooler compressor connector.</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>Remove the 4 bolts and disconnect the compressor from the engine.</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>Support the cooler compressor securely.</ptxt>
</s2>
</content1>
</s-1>
<s-1 id="RM000000VX301MX_01_0007" proc-id="RM21Q0EV__00000I600000">
<ptxt>REMOVE NO. 1 COMPRESSOR MOUNTING BRACKET
</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<s2>
<ptxt>Remove the 5 bolts and No. 1 compressor mounting bracket.</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="A099203E02" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
</s2>
</content1></s-1>
<s-1 id="RM000000VX301MX_01_0003" proc-id="RM21Q0EV__000005E00000">
<ptxt>REMOVE CRANKSHAFT POSITION SENSOR</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<s2>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="A099147E04" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
<ptxt>Disconnect the sensor connector.</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>Disconnect the connector from the connector bracket.</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>Detach the harness clamp.</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>Remove the bolt and sensor.</ptxt>
</s2>
</content1>
</s-1>
</subpara>
</para>
</ttl>
</section>
</servcat>
